
==== Sput - Simple, Portable Unit Testing Framework for C/C++ ====


==   Prerequisites and Dependencies   ==

None.


==   Installing Sput   ==

Just copy the shipped sput.h header file to you project folder.


==   Further Information   ==

Sput Tutorial
    A tutorial is included in the distribution: tutorial.txt.

Sput Website
    http://www.lingua-systems.com/unit-testing/

